      "zh": "9.3x64 毫米狩猎用软尖弹，配有重 17.4 克的半被甲弹头。该款弹药主要针对狩猎大型动物设计，在中距离的停止作用相当出色，强大的末端性能使其命中目标后能够造成恐怖的毁伤。",
      "en": "A 9.3x64mm Soft Point hunting cartridge loaded with a 17.4 gram semi-jacketed bullet. The bullet delivers increased stopping power at medium ranges and is intended for hunting large game, as it provides strong terminal performance and can cause severe incapacitating wounds on impact."
